{"title":"铜匠担","authors":["臧克家"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":12,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"铜匠担"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"臧克家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咏吉福庚同志1942—1948年秘密为新四军修造枪弹的铜匠担"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小小一担铜匠担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是一座兵工厂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它不固定在地下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"担在一双铁肩上！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走了东乡走西乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修锅补碗是虚幌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁锤私下立大志："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为人民打天下尽力量！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地上一片黑黝黝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炉子里冒着红火光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"残废枪支挺起了身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自造的子弹装进膛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天的大炮万门并列，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们珍惜当年的一支枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人已经成了灰烬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风箱仿佛还呼呼地响。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}